data.description: Lovely 4 bedroom/2.5 bathroom home located in the Oakland Farm neighborhood of Inman. Open up the front door to the open concept living, dining and kitchen area. The kitchen features a large island with bar height seating, a built-in microwave, a smooth cooktop, a dishwasher and allows access to the back patio overlooking the spacious backyard. The main floor also has a half bathroom and a room that could be a playroom/flex space or a private home office. Moving upstairs, the owner’s suite features a walk-in closet, and a full bathroom. The full bathroom is complete with a double sink vanity and a walk-in shower. 3 additional bedrooms, 1 full bathroom and a laundry room also make up the 2nd story of the home. Make this one your own and schedule a showing today!
